## ✅ Test for `AuthTransaction`

```java
class AuthTransactionTest {

    @Test
    void shouldSetAndGetFields() {
        AuthTransaction tx = new AuthTransaction();

        tx.setState("state");
        tx.setNonce("nonce");
        tx.setCodeVerifier("verifier");
        tx.setAppId("appId");
        tx.setRedirectUri("redirect");
        tx.setPostLoginRedirectUrl("postRedirect");
        tx.setCreatedAt(Instant.now());

        assertEquals("state", tx.getState());
        assertEquals("nonce", tx.getNonce());
        assertEquals("verifier", tx.getCodeVerifier());
        assertEquals("appId", tx.getAppId());
    }
}
```

