## ✅ Test for `AppConfigResponse`

```java
class AppConfigResponseTest {

    @Test
    void shouldSetAndGetFields() {
        AppConfigResponse config = new AppConfigResponse();

        config.setAppId("app1");
        config.setEnabled(true);
        config.setClientId("client");
        config.setClientSecret("secret");
        config.setIssuerUri("issuer");
        config.setRedirectUri("redirect");
        config.setScopes(List.of("openid"));
        config.setPostLoginRedirectUrl("postRedirect");
        config.setCookieName("cookie");
        config.setSessionTtlSeconds(300L);

        assertEquals("app1", config.getAppId());
        assertTrue(config.isEnabled());
        assertEquals("client", config.getClientId());
    }
}
```

